      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "How do I use AVAnnotate?",
          "textSize": "heading-two"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The AVAnnotate website provides a helpful "
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "url": "https://av-annotate.org/how-to-use/",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Quick Start"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " guide. This guide is a solid starting point for both beginners and experienced GitHub users."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The "
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "url": "https://avannotate.github.io/documentation/",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "AVAnnotate Documentation"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " provides more in-depth resources and information."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The "
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "url": "https://github.com/orgs/AVAnnotate/discussions/",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "AVAnotate Discussions Board"
            }
